# AI Learning Path Generator

## What this is
A full stack web app that generates personalized week-by-week 
learning roadmaps for any skill using AI.

## Stack
- Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js, Express
- AI: Groq API (LLaMA 3.3 70B)
- Deploy: Netlify

## Folder structure
- /client — React frontend
- /server — Node/Express backend

## Rules
- Always use async/await, never .then()
- Never use var, use const and let only
- Keep React components under 150 lines
- Always handle loading and error states
- Never hardcode API keys, always use process.env